Achievements.Description: Navigate the Abandoned Mill without hitting any obstacles.

Achievements.Name: Maximum Firepower

Achievements.Name: Treasure Hunter
Achievements.Description: Find and dig up ten buried items.

Achievements.Description: In a 4 player game, resuscitate each of your fallen comrades at least once.
